**  TBL1/TBL2 (UPDATE /NAME)
0-CANCEL
1-CHANGE
2-ADD
**  ERR
E-01 UPDATE INSTRUCTION ISN'T RIGHT
E-02 INPUT INTRAL COMPANY PART NO.
E-03 ADD WAS APPOINTED, BUT IT EXISTS IN M/F
E-04 CHANGE WAS APPOINTED, BUT THERE IS NOT IT IN M/F
E-05 CHANGE WAS APPOINTED, BUT IT'S CANCELLED ALREADY IN M/F
E-06 CANCEL WAS APPOINTED, BUT THERE IS NOT IT IN M/F
E-07 CANCEL WAS APPOINTED, BUT IT'S CANCELLED ALREADY IN M/F
E-08 INPUT USER CODE
E-09 USER CODE ISN'T RIGHT
E-10 INPUT MONTHLY SETTING NUMBER
E-11 INPUT DATE OF START PRODUCTION
E-12 DATE OF START PRODUCTION ISN'T RIGHT
E-13 PROD ORDER BOOK RECEIPT DAY ISN'T RIGHT
E-14 INPUT DAY ISN'T RIGHT
E-15 CONTAINER TYPE MUST BE THE ALPHABET
E-16 ANSWER DAY ISN'T RIGHT
E-17 APPOINTMENT DAY ISN'T RIGHT
